This theme comes with [[*user Woedenaz]]'s [[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:toggle-sidebar-bhl| BHL Toggle Sidebar]]] and [[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/component:centered-header-bhl| BHL Centered Header]]]. It looks very bad without those things. This theme also extends from his [[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/theme:extra-black-highlighter-theme| Extra Black Highlighter Theme]]].

[[=]]
+ Formatting Examples
[[/=]]

What's this? A horizontal line! "@@-----@@" You make it with four, technically, but five is nicer.

-----

Titles. But not subtitles. Or header titles. Use the "+" to make 'em.

